#This is all about how to create ansible playbook.
playbook are devided int the follwing section.
1_ Target section (Here we will define targeted nodes )
2_ Variable section (This is optional variable is basically used to ignore hard-coding)
3_ Tasks section (List of modules that we need to RUN)

#Most important playbook are written in yaml format (Human readable data serialization language) extension shuld be .yaml or .yml
Syntax
start with three hypens
--- 
- hosts: ios_routers
  connection: ssh, local,
  gather_facts: yes or no

  tasks:
  module_name:
     
...
End with three dots but this is optional not mandatory.
